text.section:
"Appurtenance and environmental setting" includes:
paved or unpaved walkways and driveways;
trees;
landscaping;
pastures;
croplands;
waterways; and
rocks.

section.section:
"Structure" includes:
a building;
a stadium;
a reviewing stand;
a platform;
staging;
an observation tower;
a radio tower;
a water tank or tower;
a trestle;
a bridge;
a pier;
paving;
a bulkhead;
a wharf;
a shed;
a coal bin;
a display sign that is visible or intended to be visible from a public way; and
a part of a structure.
